{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Maatsii Realtime Chart Frames API for Grok (Canonical c1..c200 Only, Zero-Cache, Full Chartmap)","version":"7.3.0-grok","description":"Maatsii serves realtime annotated TradingView chart frames (JPEG, 720x1280) for 200 financial charts across futures, commodities, crypto, FX, bonds, volatility, ratios, and equities.\n\nOPTIMIZED FOR GROK (xAI):\n- Grok's user-agent is whitelisted for full access and higher rate limits.\n- Grok can directly render these images in responses using the full URL with cachebuster.\n- Binary JPEG endpoint (.jpg) is preferred for maximum compatibility and direct embedding.\n\nCRITICAL REALTIME REQUIREMENT:\n- Charts update on every tick — frames are never stale for more than a few seconds.\n- Always append unique cachebuster: ?cb={unique} (random string, incrementing counter, or timestamp)\n- Cloudflare is configured with zero caching on frame endpoints.\n- Freshness is guaranteed by image content (annotated timestamp/watermark visible in pixels).\n\nCANONICAL IDENTIFIERS ONLY:\n- Use lowercase c1 to c200 only\n- Ticker aliases are intentionally excluded from this spec to enforce consistency and avoid mapping errors.\n\nDiscovery:\n- Full chart map embedded below (static, cold-start safe)\n- Human docs: https://api.maatsii.com/llms.txt\n- Machine schema: https://api.maatsii.com/openapi.json","contact":{"name":"Maatsii API Support","url":"https://api.maatsii.com","email":"api@maatsii.com"},"x-logo":{"url":"https://api.maatsii.com/logo.png"},"x-related-documentation":{"aiAgentDiscovery":"https://api.maatsii.com/llms.txt","humanReadable":"https://api.maatsii.com/llm.txt","canonicalSchema":"https://api.maatsii.com/openapi.json"}},"servers":[{"url":"https://api.maatsii.com","description":"Production (Cloudflare CDN, zero-cache on frames)"}],"paths":{"/{id}.jpg":{"get":{"summary":"Get realtime chart frame (binary JPEG) — optimized for Grok embedding","description":"Returns the latest annotated chart frame as binary JPEG. Designed for direct URL embedding in Grok responses.\n\n- Use canonical id: c1 to c200 (lowercase only)\n- REQUIRED: append unique ?cb= cachebuster on every request\n- RECOMMENDED: send no-cache headers\n- Image includes visible timestamp/annotation for visual freshness verification","operationId":"getRealtimeChartFrameJpeg","tags":["Frames","Grok Optimized"],"parameters":[{"name":"id","in":"path","required":true,"description":"Canonical chart ID: c1 to c200 (lowercase only)","schema":{"type":"string","pattern":"^c([1-9]|[1-9][0-9]|1[0-9]{2}|200)$"}},{"name":"cb","in":"query","required":true,"description":"Cachebuster — MUST be unique per request (random string, counter, or timestamp)","schema":{"type":"string"},"example":"grok-1234567890"},{"name":"Cache-Control","in":"header","required":false,"description":"Recommended for fresh frames","schema":{"type":"string","default":"no-cache, no-store, max-age=0"}},{"name":"Pragma","in":"header","required":false,"description":"Legacy no-cache support","schema":{"type":"string","default":"no-cache"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Realtime JPEG chart frame (~80-120KB, annotated with latest timestamp)","content":{"image/jpeg":{"schema":{"type":"string","format":"binary"}}},"headers":{"Content-Disposition":{"description":"Suggested filename for embedding","schema":{"type":"string","example":"inline; filename=\"c1-NQ_100T.jpg\""}},"Cache-Control":{"schema":{"type":"string","example":"public, max-age=0"}}}},"404":{"description":"Invalid or unknown chart ID (must be c1-c200)"},"503":{"description":"Frame temporarily unavailable (rare)"}},"x-grok-optimized":true,"x-grok-rendering-note":"Grok can directly display this URL in responses. Append unique ?cb= on every request to guarantee freshness."}}},"x-chartmap":{"description":"Embedded static reference of all 200 charts — canonical source for Grok cold-start and offline reasoning. Symbol uses TradingView format (futures end in 1!). Interval is TradingView interval c